videos.description: T.J. Cromer drives and gets the tough and-1 layup to fall.
videos.headline: ETSU guard Cromer pulls the Buccaneers to within four

videos.description: T.J. Cromer drives and gets the tough and-1 layup to fall.
videos.headline: ETSU guard Cromer pulls the Buccaneers to within four

videos.description: E. Tennessee State guard T.J. Cromer grabs the loose rebound and takes it back the length of the court for the tough layup.
videos.headline: Cromer goes coast-to-coast for two for ETSU

videos.description: Spartans center R.J. White gets the pass down low and slams it home for the dunk and the foul.
videos.headline: White throws down the dunk for UNC Greensboro, plus the foul

videos.description: T.J. Cromer kicks it out to teammate David Burrell, who knocks down the three to give ETSU the lead in the second half.
videos.headline: Cromer finds Burrell for three as he falls to the ground

videos.description: A.J. Merriweather knocks down the big 3 to put ETSU up by eight.
videos.headline: Merriweather buries the huge 3 to increase ETSU's lead

videos.description: Desonta Bradford drains the big 3-pointer to give the Buccaneers a 10 point with under three minutes to go.
videos.headline: ETSU's Bradford nails clutch 3 to add to lead late

videos.description: UNC Greensboro's Francis Alonso misses a wide open 3-pointer late as the Spartans fall to ETSU.
videos.headline: Greensboro's Alonso comes up short on the game-tying 3.

videos.description: East Tennessee State University returns to the tournament as they defeat UNC Greensboro 79-74.
videos.headline: ETSU punches their ticket to the big dance

videos.description: Sean Farnham and Jason Benetti break down ETSU's 79-74 win as the Buccaneers return to the big dance.
videos.headline: Postgame breakdown: ETSU vs. UNC Greensboro
